>Well, Unix is a lot more than the commands. If the directory structures were
>similar to Unix's directory structures, if I could use the Unix Makefiles
>without having to completely create a new makefile for OS/2 (Unix programs
>almost never come with an OS/2 makefile), and if almost ALL widely used
>Unix utilities were ported in a decent form (I've seen some horrendous 
